metadata.name: 01 Baby Raccoon
metadata.description: Meet the newest addition to your NFT collection, the Baby Raccoon! This adorable creature is just starting out on its journey through life. With its playful and curious nature, the baby raccoon is always up for an adventure. With its round, fluffy tail, big curious eyes, and tiny little paws, this raccoon is the epitome of cuteness. Its fur is a warm, rich brown color, and its markings are a striking black, making it stand out in any collection. This character is the perfect starting point for anyone looking to build a collection of cute and quirky raccoons. So why wait? Start your journey now and add the baby raccoon to your collection today!
